WEBVTT

00:24.760 --> 00:28.780
V It is reported commonly that there was fornication

00:28.780 --> 00:35.700
and such fornication as is not so much as named among the Gentiles, that one should have his

00:35.700 --> 00:42.300
father's wife. And ye are puffed up, and have not rather mourned, that he that hath done this deed

00:42.300 --> 00:48.600
might be taken away from among you. For I verily, as absent in body, but present in spirit,

00:48.960 --> 00:54.160
have judged already as though I were present, concerning him that hath so done this deed.

00:54.680 --> 00:59.520
In the name of our Lord Jesus Christ, when ye are gathered together, and my spirit,

00:59.820 --> 01:06.380
with the power of our Lord Jesus Christ, to deliver such an one unto Satan for the destruction of the

01:06.380 --> 01:12.880
flesh, that the spirit may be saved in the day of the Lord Jesus. Your glorying is not good.

01:13.200 --> 01:18.800
Know ye not that a little leaven leaveneth the whole lump? Purge out therefore the old leaven,

01:18.800 --> 01:25.220
that ye may be a new lump, as ye are unleavened. For even Christ our Passover is sacrificed for

01:25.220 --> 01:31.120
us. Therefore let us keep the feast, not with old leaven, neither with the leaven of malice

01:31.120 --> 01:38.580
and wickedness, but with the unleavened bread of sincerity and truth. I wrote unto you in an epistle

01:38.580 --> 01:44.060
not to company with fornicators, yet not altogether with the fornicators of this world,

01:44.060 --> 01:51.140
or with the covetous, or extortioners, or with idolaters, for then must ye needs go out of the

01:51.140 --> 01:57.280
world. But now I have written unto you not to keep company, if any man that is called a brother,

01:57.660 --> 02:04.440
be a fornicator, or covetous, or an idolater, or a railler, or a drunkard, or an extortioner,

02:04.760 --> 02:10.720
with such an one know not to eat. For what have I to do, to judge them also that are without?

02:10.720 --> 02:16.960
Do not ye judge them that are within? But them that are without, God judgeth. Therefore put

02:16.960 --> 02:24.720
away from among yourselves that wicked person. Chapter 6. Dare any of you, having a matter

02:24.720 --> 02:31.260
against another, go to law before the unjust, and not before the saints? Do we not know that

02:31.260 --> 02:36.880
the saints shall judge the world? And if the world shall be judged by you, are ye unworthy

02:36.880 --> 02:43.740
to judge the smallest matters? Know we not that we shall judge angels? How much more things that

02:43.740 --> 02:50.220
pertain to this life? If then ye have judgments of things pertaining to this life, set them to judge

02:50.220 --> 02:57.160
who are least esteemed in the church. I speak to your shame. Is it so that there is not a wise man

02:57.160 --> 03:04.120
among you? No, not one that shall be able to judge between his brethren. But brother goeth to law

03:04.120 --> 03:10.720
with brother, and that before the unbelievers. Now therefore there is utterly a fault among you,

03:11.120 --> 03:18.160
because ye go to law one with another. Why do we not rather take wrong? Why do ye not rather suffer

03:18.160 --> 03:26.840
yourselves to be defrauded? Nay, ye do wrong and defraud, and that your brethren. Know we not that

03:26.840 --> 03:33.340
the unrighteous shall not inherit the kingdom of God? Be not deceived, neither fornicators,

03:33.340 --> 03:40.280
nor idolaters, nor adulterers, nor effeminate, nor abusers of themselves with mankind,

03:41.020 --> 03:48.000
nor thieves, nor covetous, nor drunkards, nor revilers, nor extortioners shall inherit the

03:48.000 --> 03:54.160
kingdom of God. And such were some of you, but ye are washed, but ye are sanctified,

03:54.480 --> 04:00.580
but ye are justified in the name of the Lord Jesus, and by the spirit of our God. All things

04:00.580 --> 04:06.460
are lawful unto me, but all things are not expedient. All things are lawful for me,

04:06.580 --> 04:13.200
but I will not be brought under the power of Aene. Meats for the belly, and the belly for meats,

04:13.760 --> 04:20.520
but God shall destroy both it and them. Now the body is not for fornication, but for the Lord,

04:20.880 --> 04:27.680
and the Lord for the body. And God hath both raised up the Lord, and will also raise up us

04:27.680 --> 04:34.460
by his own power. Know ye not that your bodies are the members of Christ? Shall I then take the

04:34.460 --> 04:41.720
members of Christ, and make them the members of Anharlot? God forbid. What? Know ye not that he

04:41.720 --> 04:49.360
which is joined to Anharlot is one body? For two, saith he, shall be one flesh. But he that is

04:49.360 --> 04:56.780
joined unto the Lord is one spirit. Flee fornication. Every sin that a man doeth is without the body,

04:56.780 --> 05:05.020
but he that cometh fornication sinneth against his own body. What? Know ye not that your body is the

05:05.020 --> 05:12.800
temple of the Holy Ghost which is in you, which ye have of God, and ye are not your own? For ye

05:12.800 --> 05:19.200
are bought with a price. Therefore glorify God in your body, and in your spirit, which are God's.

05:26.800 --> 05:29.600
March 2011

